{"tid":856464,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"她拿媽媽的凡士林塗嘴唇　結果抹了肛門鬆弛劑","createTime":"2018-10-10T15:06:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-10T15:16:46.000Z","uid":121831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"326c1a301cd7df95f45211bca6aada5c4001e9b3","tid":856464,"uid":121831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T15:06:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20181009/1444030/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20181009%2F1444030%2F&d=GMKqUHOqK0NWwf0BctgWdTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=64498b48\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20181009%2F1444030%2F&h=fbbdb5a6\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20181009/1444030/</a><br />\n東西要往嘴裡放、身上抹之前，還是先確認到底拿了什麼吧。最近在社群平台上有段熱門短片，一名女子因為嘴唇乾裂，到媽媽房間想找凡士林(Vaseline)抹抹嘴唇，找到一個小小粉紅色藥盒，打開就往嘴唇抹上。結果女孩立刻感覺自己的嘴唇麻痺，完全失去感覺，趕緊找媽媽來問，才知道她抹了媽媽的「肛門鬆弛劑」(anal relaxant)。<br />\n<br />\n不慌不忙的哥倫比亞籍女孩查莫洛(Dayana Chamorro)，拿起手機開始自拍，片段中可見她邊忍著笑邊敘述整件糗事，「我把這個抹上嘴唇......結果我的嘴唇『睡著了』」，說到這裡她已經笑到岔氣，「我把媽媽的肛門鬆弛膏......抹在嘴唇上了」，查莫洛說到這裡已經笑到流淚，旁邊的女性(應該是她媽媽)也跟著大笑，最後不忘給出中肯建議：「在使用或吃任何東西前，務必確認，別讓這種事發生在妳身上」！<br />\n影片短時間內已經有超過1千3百萬次瀏覽，許多網友都說自己「笑到哭出來」，也有人留言表示「喜歡她的笑聲」。（於慶中／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181009/640_00bed6a7414c1b74a35e100935e3789d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181009%2F640_00bed6a7414c1b74a35e100935e3789d.jpg&h=d19680bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n查莫洛在媽媽房間找到這個小藥盒，以為裡面裝的是凡士林，拿起來就往嘴唇上抹。翻攝自《每日星報》<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181009/640_434ce7078f9db2cd30cdfecc784f5ccf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181009%2F640_434ce7078f9db2cd30cdfecc784f5ccf.jpg&h=c7db2db8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n查莫洛邊說邊忍笑，最後笑到哭出來。翻攝自《每日星報》<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我想知佢呀媽點解要用肛門鬆弛劑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪緊得滯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40bba8b91ad33a1752d0292fb20fda7fbe0d887e","tid":856464,"uid":121831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T15:08:29.000Z","msg":"屌 睇完條片見到佢老母<br />\n當我#1個句冇講過"},{"pid":"6e05d65a0f275a0111bb629e0c513a545d31f249","tid":856464,"uid":116704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T15:15:03.000Z","msg":"肛門鬆弛膏用途係..."},{"pid":"bbd9839e624beab88e128f8b7cc7a750ff306c54","tid":856464,"uid":3962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T15:16:32.000Z","msg":"鬼婆咁中意屌屎忽"},{"pid":"6704437544f4c74df161da9aa6001381fcd14c65","tid":856464,"uid":106426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T15:16:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}